    <item>
      <title>越来越多的风力发电厂停产，德国风力发电目标面临威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/germany-s-wind-power-goals-threatened-as-more-farms-go-offline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[补贴计划结束后，德国首次关闭的陆上风电场数量超过新增数量，但为了实现雄心勃勃的气候目标，德国仍然扩大了其最重要能源的产能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/germany-s-wind-power-goals-threatened-as-more-farms-go-offline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 10:39:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
